summary: I used to wonder if the creators of my favorite movies and shows cared about me and the fans in my country. Cause its a small...
body:
I used to wonder if the creators of my favorite movies and shows cared about me and the fans in my country. Cause its a small and poor country. And I was like yea they probably do they care about all fans right? Right?

WRONG

I know that the Russos and Kevin fiege don’t control this but, seriously? You don’t even talk about it? Not even a post. Nothing.

And above that they go for a press tour in INDIA!

The Fandom in my country is literally begging for their help and no one even turns to look at us?

Is this how much you care about your Fandom marvel?

We don’t even get marvel and disney movies on Netflix and now we won’t get them in theaters either.

THANKS FOR LETTING US BE A PART OF THIS JOURNEY AND DITCHING US NEAR THE END.
